calculate(boolean, J2R) - Static method in class J2R.SingeltonTestMainStart
Contains the method calculate which calculates the V-Matrix and Min/Max This method calls methods of the PrepareforR class to get the information of WindowRelevantFactors Then the method calls both controllers to build and run the code At the end of the method the windowDimensionless Windows will be build up with all necessary values
